        "label": "DatoCMS API token",
        "generateUrl": "https://www.datocms.com/docs/content-management-api/authentication",
        "setup": "Go to your project administrative area at [Project Settings → API Tokens](https://www.datocms.com/docs/content-management-api/authentication) and create an API token. Every project includes a read-only token by default; create a custom token and role if you need write/delete or narrower permissions. Use this token for the CMA, and for the CDA make sure the token also has the `Access the Content Delivery API` or `Access the Content Delivery API in Preview Mode` flag enabled.",
